    "tag": "JK",
    "text": "This is my mother, Malka Kempler. The picture, to the best of my understanding, was taken in Krakow, possibly about 1938 when she was 40 years old. She died at 44. She was taken from Bochnia to someplace-- I don't know where, whether she was killed in Bochnia or taken to Auschwitz or some of the other places. But this was-- she died then with her mother, my grandmother, back in 1942. [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
